Package application.controller

Class PhotoDialogController

java.lang.Object
application.controller.PhotoDialogController
public class PhotoDialogController extends Object
Controller for the photo dialog screen that allows users to: - View photo details - Edit tags (add, remove, modify) - Navigate through photos in the album - Move or copy a photo between albums This is a modal window launched from within an album.
